027f4cde707af44c599236b57fbb49cd6efe0677.query:
INSERT INTO peer_announces(
  info_hash,
  peer_id,
  ip,
  port,
  uploaded,
  downloaded,
  remaining,
  event,
  last_update_ts
)
VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, $7, $8, $9)
ON CONFLICT (info_hash, peer_id) DO UPDATE
  SET
    ip = $3,
    port = $4,
    uploaded = $5,
    downloaded = $6,
    remaining = $7,
    event = $8,
    last_update_ts = $9;

1742a5c13677ee38e720979640dde7a26440d0a7.query:
SELECT
  info_hash,
  COUNT(*) FILTER (WHERE remaining = 0) AS complete,
  COUNT(*) FILTER (WHERE remaining <> 0) AS incomplete
FROM
  peer_announces
WHERE info_hash = ANY($1)
GROUP BY info_hash

39107c7781e484c9f020df97fad59b1ce06c6b1d.query:
SELECT info_hash, is_allowed
FROM info_hashes
WHERE info_hash = $1

be47349b03df4e8a060cb4c1895994e6302f2c21.query:
SELECT peer_id, ip, port
FROM peer_announces
WHERE
  info_hash = $1 AND ip <> $2
  AND last_update_ts > $3
